The '''Grotesque Guardians''' are [[gargoyle]] [[slayer bosses]] that reside at the top of the [[Slayer Tower]].
[[File:Fighting_Grotesque_Guardians.png|thumb|300px|A player fights the [[Grotesque Guardians]] on the Slayer Tower's roof.]]
In order to access and fight them, the player must be assigned [[gargoyles]] as a [[Slayer task]] or be assigned a Grotesque Guardians [[boss task]]. Prior to this, the player must also obtain a [[brittle key]] to permanently unlock the gate. The brittle key has a 1/150 drop rate from regular gargoyles (on task only) and [[marble gargoyle]]s.

''Like gargoyles, players '''must''' bring a [[rock hammer]], [[granite hammer]], or [[rock thrownhammer]] to finish them off.''

